Uxn/Varvara emulator for Kolibri OS

Based on https://github.com/chmod222/zuxn

compile: zig build --release=fast
result: zig-out/bin/uxn
run: uxn SOME.rom
control:
  Up/Down/Left/Right
  Ctrl/Shift/Alt/Home
  F1: change scale (1x, 2x, 3x)

